text.section:
A record shall be kept in the Office of the State Comptroller giving:
the name of the officer or employee for whom any individual bond is issued;
the name of the agency in which the officer or employee is employed or the name of the agencies covered under a blanket bond program;
the name of the company issuing the bond; and
the amount, date, and time of expiration of the bond and of any certificate renewing the bond.
